  "title": "singer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Performs live singing as the main attraction in the live house.</li>\n  <li>Engages the audience and builds a connection through performance.</li>\n  <li>Rehearses regularly with the band and follows the music director’s guidance.</li>\n  <li>Takes care of vocal health and maintains consistent stage presence.</li>\n  <li>May also handle promotional appearances, fan interactions, or social media engagement.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Skills Required</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Strong vocal technique and versatility across genres.</li>\n  <li>Charisma, stage presence, and audience engagement.</li>\n  <li>Stamina for frequent live shows.</li>\n  <li>Teamwork with musicians, sound crew, and directors.</li>\n</ul>",
